      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WILD STAR (2) placed last time (23.12) at Mt Gambier in a Grade 4/5, finishing third and beaten 3.5 lengths. Has already won two times from this draw. With a clean break looks hard to beat. ROLL ON COASTER (3) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by one length at this track in a handy 19.51 beating American Indian. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. BELLA MAC (1) missed the frame latest when sixth at Gawler (23.08) but scored four back at Gawler (23.05). Solid record here at the distance winning six races. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings six times from 11 starts. Should play a prominent role. RIPPIN' PEDRO (8) has a solid strike rate at this distance.",
